'''葛萊分多毛圓蛛'''（學名：''{{sname|Eriovixia gryffindori}}''），[[蜘蛛目|蜘蛛目]]下[[圓蛛科|圓蛛科]]（金蛛科）所屬<ref name="Ahmed2016">{{cite journal|last1=Ahmed|first1=Javed|last2=Khalap|first2=Rajashree|last3=Sumukha|first3=JN|title=A new species of dry foliage mimicking ''Eriovixia'' Archer, 1951 from central Western Ghats, India (Araneae: Araneidae)|journal=Indian Journal of Arachnology|date=2016|volume=5|issue=1-2|pages=24–27|url=http://indianarachnology.com/ija/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ija_2016_v5_n1_2_p7_24_27.pdf|accessdate=11 December 2016|publisher=Indian Society of Arachnology|issn=2278-1587|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161212031703/http://indianarachnology.com/ija/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ija_2016_v5_n1_2_p7_24_27.pdf|archivedate=2016-12-12}}</ref>。2015年10月，[[印度|印度]]博物學家賈偉德·阿邁德（Javed Ahmed）等3人於印度西南部的[[西高止山脈|西高止山脈]]（[[卡纳塔克邦|卡纳塔克邦]]）發現，2016年發表。由於，其外觀與小說《[[哈利·波特|哈利·波特]]》[[哈利波特中的魔法物品|魔法物品]]中的[[霍格沃茨魔法学校|霍格沃茨魔法学校]][[分類帽|分類帽]]相似，因而根據「[[高錐客·葛來分多|高錐客·葛來分多]]」予以命名。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/New-spider-named-after-Harry-Potter-character/articleshow/55918535.cms|title=New spider named after Harry Potter character|first=|date=11 december 2016|work=TNN|publisher=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|accessdate=2016-12-21|author=Vijay Singh|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930091934/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/New-spider-named-after-Harry-Potter-character/articleshow/55918535.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://pansci.asia/archives/flash/111427|title=分類帽 4 ni ! 以哈利波特角色命名的新種蜘蛛|accessdate=2016-12-25|author=valerie hung|date=2016-12-24|publisher=[[PanSci_泛科學|PanSci 泛科學]]|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028114402/https://pansci.asia/archives/flash/111427|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161215/1013261/|title=波特迷快看！　深山發現「分類帽」蜘蛛|first=|date=2015-12-15|work=|publisher=[[